                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds westerly 15 to 25 km/h.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-04-11T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-12T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-10T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-11T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds westerly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light before dawn then becoming west to southwesterly 25 to 35 km/h in the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to around 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
                <text type="fire_danger">Moderate</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 9:40am to 2:40pm, UV Index predicted to reach 5 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-04-12T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-13T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-11T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-12T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower, most likely in the morning. Winds southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h becoming light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 10 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-04-13T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-14T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-12T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-13T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to around 9 with daytime temperatures reaching around 20.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-04-14T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-15T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-13T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-14T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Light winds becoming west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day then becoming light during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 7 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
